  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t影片讲述了第八号当铺是一间与别人不同的当铺，典当的不止是金银珠宝，大屋楼契，而是一个人的四肢、内脏、运气、机遇、快乐，以及灵魂，价值高昂，其中爱情，亲情，友情是价格最昂贵的。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t那么对你来说什么是最珍贵的？爱情，亲情，友情，亦或是事业，健康？</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe most important thing to me is a heart that never dies. It does not mean that I am going to be immortal and eternal. It is, well, a mind that is still able to be inspired, a spirit that is entitled to exerting her right, a head that is clear who is evil and bright. To realize this goal, I need love that teaches me how to be tough and tender, I need families and friends who pat my back when I am weeping and laugh and cry when I go <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/ecstasy\" target=\"_blank\">ecstasy</a> and I need a healthy body that is ready to follow the willing heart's instruction. I cherish one thing, but only if everything is fine, my one thing can be done.</p>\n<p>\n\tThings that are able to buy will never be a free lunch. Things that are unable to buy will never be attained by money, power, or mysterious <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/demonic\" target=\"_blank\">demonic</a> force. So We had better cherish right here, right now, the things that we already have.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAs to me, the family is the most important just because when you get lost in your life, you can find encouragement to meet obstacle from the family. If you succeed in your industry but no one would like to share with you, what does it mean? As Lev Tolstoy writes in his novel: all happy family are alike but every unhappy family has its own unhappiness. Sometimes, whether the family is soundful has great impact on a child's lifetime. If he is born in a single-parent family, he may have difference from other children more or less. Hence, creating a good atomsphere is vital to a growth of a person.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例3：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHere is what I did once to find out my core value. First, write down one thing I cherished on each small paper cards, such as : health, happiness, efficiency, integrity, courage, perseverance, love, money etc. And then each time pull out one cards by asking &quot;if I have to give up one of them, which value should I abandon&quot; , repeat this question until you find it is impossible to drop off any one of the remaining cards. Then that is your core value. I thought this might apply here.<br />\n\tI remember one of those final cards is to be happy, which is one of my guiding values when I making choice. Life itself is already miserable enough, like a cup of black coffee, so there is no need to add any bitterness. Why don&rsquo;t we laugh loudly, even in a big difficult situation. &ldquo;Alter what is changeable and accept what is mutable, but first of all, get the wisdom to recognize them.&rdquo; This is the most intelligent words I have heard before. Since all problems find their way to go by positive actions rather than tears, I can&rsquo;t figure out one reason why these so-called dilemmas steal our happiness at most times. I want to be happy, also, I&rsquo;d like to see people around me are happy too, if they aren&rsquo;t, I even feel a responsibility to cheer them up. Maybe this is the reason I consider it as one thing that I cherished most.</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/869756/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p592515/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p592515\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p593230/\">为报复骗子 英国男子用短信发莎士比亚全集</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p593591/\">美国第一夫人米歇尔北大演讲全文+视频</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p588660/\">警惕！6大坏习惯毁掉你一整晚睡眠</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p593295/\">米歇尔访华与彭丽媛会面 第一夫人时尚比拼</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p591862/\">2014年英语专八考后交流大吐槽！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p593264/\">生活很心酸？8招支撑你度过困难时期</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p592756/\">破冰英语40句：5分钟和陌生人成为朋友</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p592752/\">乱世佳人：克里米亚美女检察长爆红网络</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p564743/\">专业升职术：这样奋斗才有意义</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=